<definitions typeLanguage="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" expressionLanguage="http://www.w3.org/1999/XPath" targetNamespace="http://www.activiti.org/test" xmlns="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:activiti="http://activiti.org/bpmn" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:omgdc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:omgdi="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI">
    <message id="injectListJSON" name="injectListJSON"/>
    <process id="UserProfile" name="UserProfile" isExecutable="true">
        <documentation>%3Cxml%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F1999%2Fxhtml%22%3E%3Cblock%20type%3D%22start%22%20id%3D%2262%22%20deletable%3D%22false%22%20x%3D%220%22%20y%3D%220%22%3E%3Cfield%20name%3D%22NAME%22%3EUserProfile%3C%2Ffield%3E%3Cnext%3E%3Cblock%20type%3D%22serviceTask%22%20id%3D%2275%22%3E%3Cfield%20name%3D%22NAME%22%3Elist%3C%2Ffield%3E%3Cfield%20name%3D%22factType%22%3ELIST_RECORDS%3C%2Ffield%3E%3Cnext%3E%3Cblock%20type%3D%22userTask%22%20id%3D%2269%22%20inline%3D%22false%22%3E%3Cfield%20name%3D%22NAME%22%3Eselect%3C%2Ffield%3E%3Cnext%3E%3Cblock%20type%3D%22serviceTask%22%20id%3D%2281%22%3E%3Cfield%20name%3D%22NAME%22%3Eread%20profile%3C%2Ffield%3E%3Cfield%20name%3D%22factType%22%3EREAD%3C%2Ffield%3E%3Cnext%3E%3Cblock%20type%3D%22serviceTask%22%20id%3D%2287%22%3E%3Cfield%20name%3D%22NAME%22%3Eread%20dossier%3C%2Ffield%3E%3Cfield%20name%3D%22factType%22%3EUPDATE%3C%2Ffield%3E%3Cnext%3E%3Cblock%20type%3D%22userTask%22%20id%3D%2288%22%20inline%3D%22false%22%3E%3Cfield%20name%3D%22NAME%22%3Ereview%3C%2Ffield%3E%3Cnext%3E%3Cblock%20type%3D%22end%22%20id%3D%2263%22%20deletable%3D%22false%22%3E%3C%2Fblock%3E%3C%2Fnext%3E%3C%2Fblock%3E%3C%2Fnext%3E%3C%2Fblock%3E%3C%2Fnext%3E%3C%2Fblock%3E%3C%2Fnext%3E%3C%2Fblock%3E%3C%2Fnext%3E%3C%2Fblock%3E%3C%2Fnext%3E%3C%2Fblock%3E%3C%2Fxml%3E</documentation>
        <startEvent id="start" name="UserProfile"/>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow1" sourceRef="start" targetRef="serviceTask10"/>
        <serviceTask id="serviceTask10" name="list" activiti:class="plugins.facts">
            <extensionElements>
                <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
                    <activiti:string>poi_list_fact</activiti:string>
                </activiti:field>
                <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
                    <activiti:expression>${LIST_RECORDSMap}</activiti:expression>
                </activiti:field>
            </extensionElements>
        </serviceTask>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow2" sourceRef="serviceTask10" targetRef="userTask5"/>
        <userTask id="userTask5" name="select" activiti:formKey="poi_select_form" activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}"/>
        <boundaryEvent id="boundarymessage3" name="Message" cancelActivity="false" attachedToRef="userTask5">
            <messageEventDefinition messageRef="injectListJSON"/>
        </boundaryEvent>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow4" sourceRef="userTask5" targetRef="serviceTask15"/>
        <serviceTask id="serviceTask15" name="read profile" activiti:class="plugins.facts">
            <extensionElements>
                <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
                    <activiti:string>poi_readprofile_fact</activiti:string>
                </activiti:field>
                <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
                    <activiti:expression>${READMap}</activiti:expression>
                </activiti:field>
            </extensionElements>
        </serviceTask>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow5" sourceRef="serviceTask15" targetRef="serviceTask20"/>
        <serviceTask id="serviceTask20" name="read dossier" activiti:class="plugins.facts">
            <extensionElements>
                <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
                    <activiti:string>poi_readdossier_fact</activiti:string>
                </activiti:field>
                <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
                    <activiti:expression>${UPDATEMap}</activiti:expression>
                </activiti:field>
            </extensionElements>
        </serviceTask>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow6" sourceRef="serviceTask20" targetRef="userTask21"/>
        <userTask id="userTask21" name="review" activiti:formKey="poi_review_form" activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}"/>
        <boundaryEvent id="boundarymessage7" name="Message" cancelActivity="false" attachedToRef="userTask21">
            <messageEventDefinition messageRef="injectListJSON"/>
        </boundaryEvent>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow8" sourceRef="userTask21" targetRef="end"/>
        <endEvent id="end" name="end"/>
    </process>
</definitions>
